  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to compare the efficacy of once daily dosing with Rhinocort Aqua
      (new formulation) against Rhinocort Aqua (current formulation) and placebo in reliving the
      symptoms of seasonal allergic rhinitis (SAR).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
